      	<p><b>Tank: </b> The tank of an e-juice pen (sometimes also referred to as a clearomizer or cartomizer) is the portion that contains the e-juice and atomizer, which screws onto the pen’s battery via threading. The most common type of threading utilized by e-juice tanks and batteries is referred to as 510. Any tank that features 510 threading is compatible with any 510 threaded batteries.</p>
