         <p><b>Atomizer: </b> Like herb pen vaporizers and wax pen vaporizers, e-juice vaporizers also utilize an atomizer as their heat source. The atomizer of an e-juice vaporizer contains the wick and heating coil. E-juice is absorbed into the wick, which is then heated by the coil to create vapor. In recent years, atomizers have been redesigned and improved to feature shorter wicks.</p>
